    "## 6. Data Cleaning & Preprocessing\n",
    "\n",
    "### Cleaning goals:\n",
    "- Convert price columns from string format (₹, commas) into numeric values\n",
    "- Convert discount percentage into numeric\n",
    "- Convert rating and rating_count to numeric\n",
    "- Handle missing values\n",
    "- Remove duplicates\n",
    "\n",
    "Clean data ensures reliable analysis and prevents misleading insights."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def clean_price(x):\n",
    "    if pd.isna(x): \n",
    "        return np.nan\n",
    "    x = str(x).replace(\"â‚¹\", \"\").replace(\",\", \"\").strip()\n",
    "    return pd.to_numeric(x, errors=\"coerce\")\n",
    "\n",
    "df[\"actual_price\"] = df[\"actual_price\"].apply(clean_price)\n",
    "df[\"discounted_price\"] = df[\"discounted_price\"].apply(clean_price)\n",
    "df[\"discount_percentage\"] = (\n",
    "    df[\"discount_percentage\"]\n",
    "    .astype(str)\n",
    "    .str.replace(\"%\", \"\")\n",
    "    .str.strip()\n",
    ")\n",
    "df[\"discount_percentage\"] = pd.to_numeric(df[\"discount_percentage\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n",
    "df[\"rating\"] = pd.to_numeric(df[\"rating\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n",
    "df[\"rating_count\"] = (\n",
    "    df[\"rating_count\"]\n",
    "    .astype(str)\n",
    "    .str.replace(\",\", \"\")\n",
    "    .str.strip()\n",
    ")\n",
    "df[\"rating_count\"] = pd.to_numeric(df[\"rating_count\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n",
    "df = df.drop_duplicates()\n",
    "df = df.dropna(subset=[\"actual_price\", \"discounted_price\", \"discount_percentage\"])\n",
    "df[\"rating\"] = df[\"rating\"].fillna(df[\"rating\"].median())\n",
    "df[\"rating_count\"] = df[\"rating_count\"].fillna(0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. Feature Engineering\n",
    "\n",
    "We create derived features to improve analysis and support scoring:\n",
    "\n",
    "### Engineered Features:\n",
    "- `discount_amount` = actual_price - discounted_price\n",
    "- `discount_ratio` = discount_amount / actual_price\n",
    "- `main_category` extracted from category hierarchy\n",
    "- optional: price_bucket (quantile-based)\n",
    "\n",
    "These features help quantify pricing strategy and deal quality."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df[\"discount_amount\"] = df[\"actual_price\"] - df[\"discounted_price\"]\n",
    "df[\"discount_ratio\"] = df[\"discount_amount\"] / df[\"actual_price\"]\n",
    "df[\"price_bucket\"] = pd.qcut(df[\"discounted_price\"], q=5, labels=[\n",
    "    \"Very Low\", \"Low\", \"Medium\", \"High\", \"Very High\"\n",
    "])\n",
    "df[\"main_category\"] = df[\"category\"].astype(str).apply(lambda x: x.split(\"|\")[0])"
   ]
